Perl dbi driver for informix
	
this is a database backend driver which allows the perl dbi to connect
to informix database servers.

you've got to have an informix client library installed on your system in
order to use this module.  you can download one from www.informix.com
(select "trials and demos", then "informix client software development
kit (csdk)") for free, but it's not free software.